{"id":291332,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/04/维权网-陈光福家凌晨又遭袭击，报警求助电话受/","date":"2013-04-30T10:45:41Z","modified":"2013-04-30T10:45:41Z","title":"维权网 | 陈光福家凌晨又遭袭击，报警求助电话受限（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员方芳报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>日凌晨</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">00</span><span>刚过，陈光福家又遭到袭击，两辆开着大前灯的车将陈光福家的院子照的如同白昼。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2:10</span><span>分，恶徒开始向陈光福家猛烈地投掷石块和瓶酒，啤酒爆炸的声音此起彼伏。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2:12</span><span>分，备受骚扰的陈光福拨打</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>报警，一个手机号码打不出去，换了一号码之后打通了，接警的人只是说知道了。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>报警后，陈光福一家人胆战心惊地躲在屋里不敢出来等待警方的到来。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>个多小时过去了，还没见警方的踪影，陈光福几次拨打</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>，电话居然无人接听！黑夜中陈光福一家人在恐惧和期盼中一直等到天亮！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>直到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6:20</span><span>分，距离陈光福家只有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>里地的双侯镇派出所的几名警察才姗姗来迟。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>陈光福说：“他们前几次往院里扔东西都是偷偷摸摸，这次开着车子还亮着灯。更奇怪的是，我用自己的电话打</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>不接。我换了号码，打通后一个小时警察没到场，我再打，这两个号码他们都不接。”</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">       </span></div>\n<div><span>陈光福告诉本网信息员，自从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日</span><span>他家已经连续</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>天遭受威胁和骚扰。今天是他第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>次打</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>报警了，但警方一直反应冷淡。恶徒们对他家的迫害还在继续，他感到恶徒对他家威胁、骚扰的手段不断升级，怕有生命危险，在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>出警前他一直在屋里不敢出去察看院子里究竟发生了什么。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>图片：陈光福家院子里被扔进的石头和瓶酒爆炸的碎片</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span><br /><span><br /></span></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-nMleZ4-IJdo/UX9OhaoK-8I/AAAAAAAAhH8/CR7gDLu3rI0/s1600/4184A067-7A4A-42A5-B607-8A72105E5B9D.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"238\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-nMleZ4-IJdo/UX9OhaoK-8I/AAAAAAAAhH8/CR7gDLu3rI0/s320/4184A067-7A4A-42A5-B607-8A72105E5B9D.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-x2BZft473Pc/UX9PmoW4sxI/AAAAAAAAhII/GgpSFZwBMTI/s1600/BEC4AC2C-E436-4EF1-A9F4-D7FD9C39BF0A.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"238\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-x2BZft473Pc/UX9PmoW4sxI/AAAAAAAAhII/GgpSFZwBMTI/s320/BEC4AC2C-E436-4EF1-A9F4-D7FD9C39BF0A.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910,19196]}